---
title: "When & where your friends meet?"
layout: "_layouts/default.twig"
---

{% block content %}
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 pb-5">
            <div class="text-center mt-4 mb-4" id="area-menu">
                {% for area in areas %}
                    <a onclick="changeMapArea('{{ area.key }}');" class="btn mr-2 btn-lg btn-outline-danger">
                        {{ area.title }}
                    </a>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>

            <div id="{{ map_id }}"></div>

            <br>

            {% include "_snippets/meetups_table.twig" %}
            {% include "_snippets/meetups_map.twig" %}

            <hr>

            <h2 class="text-center pt-4 pb-4">
                Get Up and Go to Meetup, Bro... Why?
            </h2>

            <p>Go out, <strong>meet new people, share your ideas in another country</strong> and grow. You'll be surprised how valuable feedback you can get on meetups abroad and how easy is to get your talk there. Pick meetup, write the organizer and go!</p>

            <p>Do you still doubt yourself? Look at
                <a href="https://www.tomasvotruba.cz/blog/2018/07/23/5-signs-should-never-have-a-talk-abroad/">5 Signs You Should Never Have a Talk Abroad</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
